# Database Rules

## Migrations

### ❌ NEVER do this in production:
```python
# Direct table creation bypasses migrations
SQLModel.metadata.create_all(engine)
```

### ✅ ALWAYS use Alembic migrations:
```bash
# Create new migration
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Add column to feature"

# Apply migrations
alembic upgrade head

# Rollback
alembic downgrade -1
```

